I really am grateful to know the worst version of you, to be able to see your pimples, and shower your ears with my rants everyday. I know I'm cheesier than pizza, I know you probably won't remember my 2a.m talks cause you already fell asleep. It's okay I love you anyway. I always find women attractive and sexy, those lips and heels. I wonder what God thought when He made us, super weak and fragile. I wonder what God thought when He made us giving birth to another hero. It's interesting how the weakest could be the strongest when everything is almost impossible, knees are numb. Many of us are struggling to move on, struggling to live alone, struggling to decide which way to go, and sometimes struggling to show the world our true colors. There's nothing to be afraid of, really. There's no need to obliterate men, really, we need each other. There won't be a better life with insecurities in it, just saying. But there will be a better day when you shake it off a bit or just loosen up a lil bit, a brighter smile at least. You must be thankful for those desirable boobs, wedding proposal and even a cute baby! Being a successful woman is best, but being a successful mother is beyond everything, and only women can do that. Wear your beautiful soul on the outside, women!
